Titolo: ARMA 2: Operation Arrowhead

Anno: 2010

Descrizione: ARMA 2: Operation Arrowhead (ARMA 2: OA; stylized as ARMA II: Operation Arrowhead) is a standalone expansion pack to Bohemia Interactive's tactical shooter ARMA 2. ARMA 2: Operation Arrowhead includes three new multiplayer maps, new vehicles and equipment, new factions, along with a new campaign.The game has sold 3.5 million copies as of February 2015.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
